    ;     of an auxiliary and of the main verb).
    ; *** It returns a new list of dependents obtained by merging the two
    ;     lists: all of these are assumed to be cases of the main verb
; %%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%% THE NEXT FUNCTIONS ARE ONLY FOR TUT %%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%
